Interface KeyIterator

All Known Implementing Classes:
KeyIteratorImpl
public interface KeyIterator

Key Iterator for memcached,use 'stats items' and 'stats cachedump' to iterate all keys,it is inefficient and not thread-safe.

Author:
dennis
